{"tid":1224303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅冠聰：緊係出啦！出佢老味呀！","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T04:03:23.000Z","uid":31341,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1914f1d66c59d337a76bd7feded2f95301e70c83","tid":1224303,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:53:56.000Z","msg":"暫緩？如果今晚政府宣佈暫緩，星期日大家仲出唔出黎呀？<br />\n<br />\n緊係出啦！出佢老味呀！<br />\n<br />\n如果政府今日同你講暫緩你就退，咁被橡膠子彈射中既示威者呢？被以「暴動罪」拘捕既示威者呢？邊個為佢地伸張正義！<br />\n<br />\n如果我地繼續行動，就意味住政府一定會持續受壓，種種不公平不公義先可以有扭轉既跡象。即使佢緩、佢撤，我地係無贏到任何野架！<br />\n<br />\n係！無！贏！到！任！何！野！ <br />\n<br />\n我地只係阻止左一個惡法，而呢個惡法本身係唔存在架。追究警暴、林鄭落台、甚至民主自由，呢啲先係我地要主動爭取嘅野。一定要繼續施壓，直至香港人得到公義為止！<br />\n<br />\n出黎呀，一鼓作氣！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1357627381056121&amp;id=100004266164397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1357627381056121%26id%3D100004266164397&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=5fdbca14\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1357627381056121&amp;id=100004266164397</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一個表態唔接受階段性勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d06acf913f4e3dcb7d66280ed0f50514c96cac","tid":1224303,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:55:15.000Z","msg":"其實612佢去咗邊"},{"pid":"072d93ceff9ecda6cd7622a21a408d928006ae29","tid":1224303,"uid":31341,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i